{"tid":141242,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"求 南山南 歌詞 wallpaper","createTime":"2017-03-02T18:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T14:59:08.000Z","uid":8202,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8664dac097d41f36d799ab708e2abd8111a3173","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:14:27.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打 <br />\n小弟係某日係youtube聽到Lng鳥屎唱左一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭都覺得首歌一般般 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但後尾法國越聽越上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到依家成日都無限loop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中有句歌詞好打動到細佬我<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n他不再和誰談論相逢的孤島<br />\n因為心裡早已荒無人煙<br />\n他的心裡再裝不下一個家<br />\n做一個只對自己說謊的啞巴<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n我覺得成首歌都好有詩意<br />\n希望有巴打可以整一張歌詞wallpaper比小弟<br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電腦wallpaper"},{"pid":"f6534d99e7466d72fae89a12aca7979e34681917","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:14:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n連登有愛"},{"pid":"81373aa3e47460ecb82c753bd753e386fff7b894","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:16:07.000Z","msg":"連登有愛"},{"pid":"94374e83c605e89c9c7a9429b38175ebbb4cb260","tid":141242,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"南山南 北海北"},{"pid":"a8ed9c02e93dc76a98296f7c04c4c3f7c2d206f8","tid":141242,"uid":81584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"正皮比首歌嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece47d9cb5777a40f1c7d4d32f84345e835e65a2","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南山南 北海北</blockquote><br />\n南山有谷堆<br />\n<br />\n屌有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fc1cbe0f6bf6bb441f39208d8cf07c534c7302","tid":141242,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:20:06.000Z","msg":"有冇聽埋專輯其他歌？"},{"pid":"b9bbfecf3af09a0a9bd8c83a4c288c8ac996ff92","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>南山南 北海北</blockquote><br />\n南山有谷堆<br />\n<br />\n屌有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南山南，北秋悲<br />\n南山有谷堆<br />\n南風喃，北海北<br />\n北海有墓碑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠一打"},{"pid":"8159eacaf696e5c051df5ebad856d42f2b51592d","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"頭先見到youtube啲留言<br />\n其中一個係<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;我寫過一首歌叫「南山南」，常有人聽完感到太悲傷，接著就問歌裡面是不是有故事。我說，你聽到這首歌的時候，它就已經和我無關了，你流下的眼淚裡面，才是自己知道的故事。&rdquo;﻿<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a643c917e5b9345c2f9a590fd782ff31b9cdf3","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇聽埋專輯其他歌？</blockquote><br />\n無呀 但想買碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9da8ea1787e8361bc1f15dd715cce62a3ce779","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:26:44.000Z","msg":"連登有愛"},{"pid":"2964773f84abb98068e045f4727a0cceba8078bd","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"董小姐<br />\n<br />\n董小姐，我也是個複雜的動物<br />\n嘴上一句帶過 心裡卻一直重複<br />\n董小姐，鼓樓的夜晚時間匆匆<br />\n陌生的人，請給我一支蘭州"},{"pid":"48017582783d2b233b2698293248d4d7ec9b2872","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:32:17.000Z","msg":"山丘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rVEMTxg_LrU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrVEMTxg_LrU&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6b10d096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rVEMTxg_LrU</a><br />\n因為不安而頻頻回首<br />\n無知地索求 羞恥于求救<br />\n不知疲倦地翻越 每一個山丘<br />\n<br />\n越過山丘 雖然已白了頭<br />\n喋喋不休 時不我予的哀愁<br />\n還未如願見著不朽<br />\n就把自己先搞丟<br />\n<br />\n越過山丘 才發現無人等候<br />\n喋喋不休 再也喚不回溫柔<br />\n為何記不得上一次是誰給的擁抱<br />\n在什麼時候"},{"pid":"4d5ffe2f870336e8ae933a03d1ac420fe524baf1","tid":141242,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:35:01.000Z","msg":"再一次聽返<br />\n感覺更深"},{"pid":"96210ab5afeba802bc698b50a5b10042aaf3e434","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再一次聽返<br />\n感覺更深</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我只係將呢首歌放入自己三十歲要聽返嘅歌list入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699afbcb42ee1a0a0c9709c152eabab04d318005","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:39:57.000Z","msg":"因為單身的緣故<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h11rUT7hJXY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh11rUT7hJXY&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0aa116b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h11rUT7hJXY</a><br />\n迎風起舞 讓月光愛撫 我為王在自己的國度<br />\n我在專心支解虛無 我把僅存慾望去骨<br />\n我像巫師得 專心練法術"},{"pid":"5e807761739c500217ca5b64b277e8876c43f00d","tid":141242,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>董小姐<br />\n<br />\n董小姐，我也是個複雜的動物<br />\n嘴上一句帶過 心裡卻一直重複<br />\n董小姐，鼓樓的夜晚時間匆匆<br />\n陌生的人，請給我一支蘭州</blockquote><br />\n你才不是一個沒有故事的女同學"},{"pid":"b365c40a05af00e7d938b8d3fa17b6080d916a01","tid":141242,"uid":60381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:02:06.000Z","msg":"用moov有得自製歌詞圖<br />\n睇下啱唔啱用<br />\nbtw聽馬啪啪一定要聽傲寒"},{"pid":"08b02abbfaacadaa45d158d6b81272b7acc71d9d","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用moov有得自製歌詞圖<br />\n睇下啱唔啱用<br />\nbtw聽馬啪啪一定要聽傲寒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭真係想求圖 但依家變左想聽大家分享"},{"pid":"1df5fa84ba46bdac503c2c1be17b9fe9fcf1c091","tid":141242,"uid":8202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:12:22.000Z","msg":"再嘈就毒啞你 分享<br />\n<br />\n傲寒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4r6nqfZ0Z3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4r6nqfZ0Z3A&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWI9%